Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把能替我保護你的人 我信任的朋友帶來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色戰士 登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}ガンバレッド是一款很老的射击游戏，1994年出版
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸の奥が高鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い声に気づいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,スタートラインは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目の前にある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ見えない道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:50.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走り始めればいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諦めるよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:55.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素敵だと思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:00.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも不安はすぐ傍で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:06.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駆け出す思いを　締め付けるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:09.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を越えて　歩き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知なる道に光を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.46,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初めてを　繰り返し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.01,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掴み取れ　明日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:21.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうさ友達が無限の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:23.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢抱きしめ　進むのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:29.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝いてる自分を信じていい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:32.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がる力に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大の愛をこめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:38.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うまま　変えた今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:44.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界乗り変え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開歌喉 高聲歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有人能注意到自己熱情的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的起跑線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然前邊的路看不到盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:50.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的朝前走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:55.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:00.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不安一直徘徊在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:06.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將自己這份雀躍的心情小心收起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:09.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來邁出自己的腳步 超越現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮前方那條未知的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.46,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成一個又一個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.01,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的雙手緊緊抓住未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:21.20,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友們快來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:23.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起擁抱無限的夢想 朝前進發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:29.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信閃閃發亮的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:32.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振奮人心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽含著滿滿的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:38.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 改變今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:44.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起擁抱新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候完全無路可走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是現在 要釋放這種力量了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}祝賀奪冠！白濱阪高中 田中大智
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:16.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなの希望が詰まったこの剣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:22.63,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,エターナルゾーンホリーブレード
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:27.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気丈を　涙を力に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:33.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　巨大な敵に立ち向かうのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:41.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever!(Forever!)(Forever!)Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:16.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝聚大家希望的這把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:22.63,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是永恆的聖潔之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:27.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將勇氣和眼淚化成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:34.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作氣 揮刀衝向強大的敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國大賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直想像著今天的場面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我也想登上大舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 賽馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為騎手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和全力奔跑的馬一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越所有人 快速衝向終點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～很帥氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們不要太鬧騰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到慶祝的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還只是第一輪比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要抱著必勝的信念去參賽啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想要浪費維也納的心血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這莫名其妙的想法算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 和奏的響葫蘆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:32.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　巨大な敵に立ち向かうのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:32.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作氣 揮刀衝向強大的敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天身體不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:54.56,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad3\4c&HA6A4A5&\bord0\fad(400,200)}第五集  {\bord2\4c&HA1D734&} {\4c&HD7EEA6&\3c&HFBFEF0&\c&H8473F7&}時而捨棄 {\c&HE3A37C&\4c&H8973F9&}時而不捨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們太鬧騰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來夏是節日積極分子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節日？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中當初為神馬開始打羽毛球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別省略啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}紗羽把badminton（羽毛球）省略成badmin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請白濱阪高中的田中大智同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到指定場地候場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振奮精神 大幹一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大智 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}是江戶時代為了鼓動民眾團結一致而喊的口號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用誓死的決心喊出口號 再在杯子裏盛上營養豐富的飲料…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有粉紅色的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉紅色…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色不也很好看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家 真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能幫我倒杯茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我做晚飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請在這邊付錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝者和田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打進八強的話 已經相當厲害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打進四強的話就可以參加全國大賽了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那順便買瓶綠茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拿一下包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做想像練習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在記憶還沒被沖淡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中是什麼時候開始打羽毛球的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是小學三年級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始參加社團活動之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大智馬上說也要參加 還想要自己的球拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小學就開始打的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不去羽毛球盛行的高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且念白高的話能騎自行車上學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前部裏也有不少成員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有我曾崇拜過的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是畢業於我們高中 之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是因為這個選手 你才開始打羽毛球的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說別省略了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是為了在夏天也不讓身體冷卻才賣熱的綠茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹些什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近好像沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 水好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是紗羽的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我志保
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒玩這個 身手遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對紗羽保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一定會馬上說 你已經不年輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年比一年囉嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就隨便找個地方放下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流汗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去沖個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是這個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是白高的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小和奏的學姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候說到這一帶不是白中就是鐮中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是小和奏的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}祝賀合唱部奪得桂冠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我大一歲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是高倉學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高倉直子現在是教導主任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把這個好好重洗一張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家以前都是合唱部的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在比賽中奪冠後拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聽媽媽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒跟她說過生病的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你瞧那孩子不是正在考試嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 接下來我會處理的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我來做今天的晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很閒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 當心點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你病倒了 嚇我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都太誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也很快就能出院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去借塊抹布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你要多加注意自己的身體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能和你一起創作歌曲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會好起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多聽聽和奏的想法和意見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我沒閒工夫做這些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起來唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這個心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神太緊張的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是考不出好水平的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這都要怪誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹你生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能一起創作歌曲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就會好起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 認真教我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不是示例嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小時候經常和我一起唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然學習也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是考試結束後也要繼續學音樂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓音樂一直常伴在和奏左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不要忘卻熱愛音樂的情懷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試不過關的話就沒有意義了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃到腰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那週六週日就你先頂著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊從週一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏 這種事情是要互相關照的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野叔叔打來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 說是又閃到腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算下週一去幫他做做農活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英彥先生又是上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也不能突然請假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要去個兩三天 沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯乾脆叫壽司來吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把屋子裏的鋼琴處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能讓給其他真心喜歡音樂的人用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想媽媽也會欣慰的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就留個小CD機就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再整理一下其他不需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騰出來的位置就放張床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我明天就打電話問問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關東地區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天從早上開始多雲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在強烈的低氣壓正向小笠原的近海處靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受此影響
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從中午到傍晚將會有暴風雨天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 補習拖到很晚的話 最好帶上雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風力好像也會加強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會有人來把鋼琴和其他東西的都拉走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我都標注清楚了 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 金魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鯨魚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金魚啦 金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:14:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯨魚啦 鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就取中間 當它是海豚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豚會唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我三點半也要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事打電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔家的手機雖然很難打通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遠野的號碼你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯叫壽司外賣也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我沒問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學後有社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的話你也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要開派對慶祝大智進入前八強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我想在下雨之前去買點東西就回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:17:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在要搞羽毛球比賽的慶功宴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中請客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 今天有點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蛋糕已經買了和奏的份了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有好大的草莓的那種哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少吃了蛋糕再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然很沒精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是討厭草莓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說她嫌我很煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是稍微有點可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(伙食費)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小虎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小虎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小～虎～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是讓你把我的雨衣拿出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的東西自己準備好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶好準考證了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有忘帶什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小虎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 別忘了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西沒啥用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都淋濕了 快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的人生之路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和我的女兒和奏一起攜手前行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管健康亦或疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管快樂亦或悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得只要與和奏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能創作出那樣的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對於我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌曲就是傳遞愛的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和奏教給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將想要傳達給和奏的思念化作歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是能和她一起歌唱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是還能聽到和奏創作的歌曲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生就完美無缺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連「我出門了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連「對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連「謝謝」也沒有說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能一起唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:14.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴れた日雨の日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:21.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんながいれば何時も笑顔になれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:27.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶の彼方まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:34.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出したりたゆたう声耳に澄まそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:40.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さぁ　手を差し伸べられて輪の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:49.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人じゃない空間で夢中になってる 時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:54.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心地よい風が吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:02.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑ったり泣いたり　歌ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉じていたココロを開いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:14.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出のフレーズ　口ずさむ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:20.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏でよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:14.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管天晴或者下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:21.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家在一起 隨時都能展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:27.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往記憶的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:34.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶往事 傾聽迴盪在耳邊的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:40.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 到伸手牽成的圓圈裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:49.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸在大家的世界裏 一起度過這夢幻般的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:54.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎面吹拂著清涼的風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:02.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們笑過 哭過 放聲高唱過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揚起心靈的風帆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:14.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱出回憶滿滿的歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:20.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏 你覺得我們最需要的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 和奏 你待會兒有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}第六集 時而微笑 時而想念
